\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Resynchronisation module measures length of Bit time segment.
 Block diagram of Resynchronronisation module is shown in Figure TODO.
 Resynchronisation module maintains register with Expected Segment Length.
 Expected segment length is loaded according to rules described in Table
 TODO.
 Expected Segment length register is always loaded upon the end of segment,
